17
00:01:36,780 --> 00:01:38,380
All that...

18
00:01:39,620 --> 00:01:41,300
All that is to come.

19
00:01:41,340 --> 00:01:45,340
But first, Aston Martin has
just launched a new car.

20
00:01:45,380 --> 00:01:48,060
And here's Richard Hammond
to tell us all about it.

21
